      <body style="background-color: lightcoral;">
        <font face="garamond" size = 4 color = "cornsilk">
        <p>1.Chose a number so the species can be shown.</p>
        <form action="/listSpecies" method="get">
            Number desired:
            <input type="text" size="2" name="limit"><br>
            Click here to show Json:
             <input type="checkbox" name="json" value="1"><br>
            <input type="submit" value="Click here to obtain the number of species">
        </form>


        <p>2.This form will provide the information about the karyotype.</p>
        <form action="/karyotype" method="get">
            Specie desired:
            <input type="text" size="12" name="specie"><br>
            Click here to show Json:
             <input type="checkbox" name="json" value="1"><br>
            <input type="submit" value="Click here to obtain info">
        </form>


         <p>3.To know the lenght of chromosome click here.</p>
        <form action="/chromosomeLength" method="get">
            Specie:
            <input type="text" size="12" name="specie"><br>
            Number:
            <input type="text" size="4" name="chromo"><br>
            Click here to show Json:
             <input type="checkbox" name="json" value="1"><br>
            <input type="submit" value="Click here to obtain the gene chosen">
        </form>

            <p>4.This form will provide the information about the Gene Sequence.</p>
            <p>Remember you have to introduce a Gene, not a number or a specie.</p>
        <form action="/geneSeq" method="get">
            Gene desired:
            <input type="text" size="12" name="gene"><br>
            Click here to show Json:
             <input type="checkbox" name="json" value="1"><br>
            <input type="submit" value="Click here to obtain info">
        </form>


            <p>5.This form will provide more information about the Gene Sequence.</p>
            <p>Remember you have to introduce a Gene, not a number or a specie.</p>
        <form action="/geneInfo" method="get">
            Gene desired:
            <input type="text" size="12" name="gene"><br>
            Click here to show Json:
             <input type="checkbox" name="json" value="1"><br>
            <input type="submit" value="Click here to obtain info">
        </form>

            <p>6.This form will provide calculations about the Gene Sequence.</p>
            <p>Remember you have to introduce a Gene, not a number or a specie.</p>
        <form action="/geneCal" method="get">
            Gene desired:
            <input type="text" size="12" name="gene"><br>
            Click here to show Json:
             <input type="checkbox" name="json" value="1"><br>
            <input type="submit" value="Click here to obtain info">
        </form>

            <p>7.This form will provide the name, end and start about the Gene Sequence.</p>
            <p>Remember you have to introduce a Gene number, not a gene name or a specie.</p>
        <form action="/geneList" method="get">
            Chromosome desired:
            <input type="text" size="12" name="chromo"><br>
            Start number:
            <input type="text" size="12" name="start"><br>
            End number:
            <input type="text" size="12" name="end"><br>
            Click here to show Json:
             <input type="checkbox" name="json" value="1"><br>
            <input type="submit" value="Click here to obtain info">
        </form>
